    <div class="reflection">
      <h3>Design Reflection</h3>
      <p>This course has been with me through multiple cycles, multiple platforms, and years of iteration. What I'm proudest of isn't any single feature, but the fact that the course genuinely supports educators and learners and continues to get better. Faculty trust it and students engage with it. The activities get requested by name. And the work of improving it genuinely excites me, because I can see the impact it has on people who are learning psychology for the first time. I was lucky enough to witness this first-hand while teaching with the course at Davidson College. Through that experience, I made critical updates that made the course easier for instructors to use.</p>
